<h2>Accessible but memorable</h2>

<p>
    Thanks to the team at Media Monks, it was smooth sailing until we had a working experience that we could let the summit attendants try. In the meantime, we addressed the logistics by building our own VR ready desktop computer and designing an easy to move tripod setup for all the sensors and cabling. The experience was available to the different groups that cycled through our UX vision presentation, as it was simple enough for everyone to have fun, with just a little bit of coaching.
</p>
